      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "fdd39b40feaf3c97",
      "text": "Moscoviada, [[Yurii Andrukhovych]]'s most successful novel, translated into many languages, is of unbroken topicality. Neo-authoritarian Russia, zealous nationalism, the glorification of the communist era, chauvinist kitsch, ideological pressure - all these ghosts are sent packing in a carnivalesque spectacle amid panicked laughter. [https://www.suhrkamp.de/buch/juri-andruchowytsch-moscoviada-t-9783518463123 suhrkamp.de] and [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Moscoviad wikipedia]"
